nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.32

Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.32 is the thirty-second issue of the 6th volume of Star Wars Comic UK, published on April 5, 2012. The magazine includes features the Top 5 Terrors and The Unusual Suspects, plus two free gifts, the Darth Maul Force Blaster and a Star Wars Fighter Pod.
The comic included the comic strip "The Fear Architects."
